articles.title: FAQ
articles.contents:
Where can I stay?
We will post hotel information soon.
What is the dress code?
Guests are encouraged to dress in cocktail attire.
What are the parking options?
Those staying in our hotel blocks can opt in to a shuttle service when we mail invitations.

articles.title: J I N A & L E S L I E
RSVP
articles.contents:
RSVP by November 7, 2024 using this link
jnlwedding.anrsvp.com
Please enter the first and last name of one member of your party. If you’re responding for you and a guest (or your family), you’ll be able to RSVP for your entire group.

Snow Tubing
Bear Creek Mountain Resort 101 Doe Mountain Ln, Macungie, PA 18062 
In lieu of a bachelor party, let’s go snow tubing the Friday before the ceremony! Everyone’s invited. The event & exact time are TBD depending on when the 2024/2025 season opens. We’ll confirm early November. Backup laser tag?
